\nI am a relatively attractive person and find myself in situations where people assume certain things about my character based on my appearance without even know me, the person.  The characteristics they feel I have are good, but how can they possibly know that without know me first?  So, I am coming from my personal experiences regarding this unfortunately dynamic.  =>
